package:graphql
class:CategoriesSpec
scenario:eetrieving information about one category

request:
```graphql
query findOneCategory {
    category(
        id: <id>
    ){
        id
        name
    }
}
```

response:
```json
{
    "data": {
    "category":
        {
        "id": <id>,
        "name": <name>
        }
    }
}
```

examples:
| should                            | id  | name         |
| --------------------------------- | --- | ------------ |
| "retrieve category with given id" | 1   | "RAM memory" |



response:
```json
{
    "data": {
    "category": null
    }
}
```

examples:
| should                                                | id  |
| ----------------------------------------------------- | --- |
| "retrieve that category with given id does not exist" | 2   |
